2621 case ARM::LDRLIT_ga_abs: 0
2622 case ARM::LDRLIT_ga_pcrel: ----
2623 case ARM::LDRLIT_ga_pcrel_ldr: ----
2624 case ARM::tLDRLIT_ga_abs: ----
2625 case ARM::t2LDRLIT_ga_pcrel: ----
2626 case ARM::tLDRLIT_ga_pcrel: { ----
2627 Register DstReg = MI.getOperand(0).getReg(); 0
2628 bool DstIsDead = MI.getOperand(0).isDead(); 0
2629 const MachineOperand &MO1 = MI.getOperand(1); 0
2630 auto Flags = MO1.getTargetFlags(); 0
2631 const GlobalValue *GV = MO1.getGlobal(); 0
2632 bool IsARM = Opcode != ARM::tLDRLIT_ga_pcrel && 0
2633 Opcode != ARM::tLDRLIT_ga_abs && 0
2634 Opcode != ARM::t2LDRLIT_ga_pcrel; ----
2635 bool IsPIC = 0
2636 Opcode != ARM::LDRLIT_ga_abs && Opcode != ARM::tLDRLIT_ga_abs; 0
2637 unsigned LDRLITOpc = IsARM ? ARM::LDRi12 : ARM::tLDRpci; 0
2638 if (Opcode == ARM::t2LDRLIT_ga_pcrel) 0
2639 LDRLITOpc = ARM::t2LDRpci; 0
2640 unsigned PICAddOpc = 0
2641 IsARM ----
2642 ? (Opcode == ARM::LDRLIT_ga_pcrel_ldr ? ARM::PICLDR : ARM::PICADD) 0
2643 : ARM::tPICADD; ----
2644 ----
2645 // We need a new const-pool entry to load from. ----
2646 MachineConstantPool *MCP = MBB.getParent()->getConstantPool(); 0
2647 unsigned ARMPCLabelIndex = 0; 0
2648 MachineConstantPoolValue *CPV; ----
2649 ----
2650 if (IsPIC) { 0
2651 unsigned PCAdj = IsARM ? 8 : 4; 0
2652 auto Modifier = (Flags & ARMII::MO_GOT) 0
2653 ? ARMCP::GOT_PREL 0
2654 : ARMCP::no_modifier; ----
2655 ARMPCLabelIndex = AFI->createPICLabelUId(); 0
2656 CPV = ARMConstantPoolConstant::Create( 0
2657 GV, ARMPCLabelIndex, ARMCP::CPValue, PCAdj, Modifier, ----
2658 /*AddCurrentAddr*/ Modifier == ARMCP::GOT_PREL); ----
2659 } else ----
2660 CPV = ARMConstantPoolConstant::Create(GV, ARMCP::no_modifier); 0
2661 ----
2662 MachineInstrBuilder MIB = ----
2663 BuildMI(MBB, MBBI, MI.getDebugLoc(), TII->get(LDRLITOpc), DstReg) 0
2664 .addConstantPoolIndex(MCP->getConstantPoolIndex(CPV, Align(4))); 0
2665 if (IsARM) 0
2666 MIB.addImm(0); 0
2667 MIB.add(predOps(ARMCC::AL)); 0
2668 ----
2669 if (IsPIC) { 0
2670 MachineInstrBuilder MIB = ----
2671 BuildMI(MBB, MBBI, MI.getDebugLoc(), TII->get(PICAddOpc)) 0
2672 .addReg(DstReg, RegState::Define | getDeadRegState(DstIsDead)) 0
2673 .addReg(DstReg) 0
2674 .addImm(ARMPCLabelIndex); 0
2675 ----
2676 if (IsARM) 0
2677 MIB.add(predOps(ARMCC::AL)); 0
2678 } ----
2679 ----
2680 MI.eraseFromParent(); 0
2681 return true; 0
2682 } ----
2683 case ARM::MOV_ga_pcrel: 0
2684 case ARM::MOV_ga_pcrel_ldr: ----
2685 case ARM::t2MOV_ga_pcrel: { ----
2686 // Expand into movw + movw. Also "add pc" / ldr [pc] in PIC mode. ----
2687 unsigned LabelId = AFI->createPICLabelUId(); 0
2688 Register DstReg = MI.getOperand(0).getReg(); 0
2689 bool DstIsDead = MI.getOperand(0).isDead(); 0
2690 const MachineOperand &MO1 = MI.getOperand(1); 0
2691 const GlobalValue *GV = MO1.getGlobal(); 0
2692 unsigned TF = MO1.getTargetFlags(); 0
2693 bool isARM = Opcode != ARM::t2MOV_ga_pcrel; 0
2694 unsigned LO16Opc = isARM ? ARM::MOVi16_ga_pcrel : ARM::t2MOVi16_ga_pcrel; 0
2695 unsigned HI16Opc = isARM ? ARM::MOVTi16_ga_pcrel :ARM::t2MOVTi16_ga_pcrel; 0
2696 unsigned LO16TF = TF | ARMII::MO_LO16; 0
2697 unsigned HI16TF = TF | ARMII::MO_HI16; 0
2698 unsigned PICAddOpc = isARM 0
2699 ? (Opcode == ARM::MOV_ga_pcrel_ldr ? ARM::PICLDR : ARM::PICADD) 0
2700 : ARM::tPICADD; ----
2701 BuildMI(MBB, MBBI, MI.getDebugLoc(), TII->get(LO16Opc), DstReg) 0
2702 .addGlobalAddress(GV, MO1.getOffset(), TF | LO16TF) 0
2703 .addImm(LabelId) 0
2704 .copyImplicitOps(MI); 0
2705 ----
2706 BuildMI(MBB, MBBI, MI.getDebugLoc(), TII->get(HI16Opc), DstReg) 0
2707 .addReg(DstReg) 0
2708 .addGlobalAddress(GV, MO1.getOffset(), TF | HI16TF) 0
2709 .addImm(LabelId) 0
2710 .copyImplicitOps(MI); 0
2711 ----
2712 MachineInstrBuilder MIB3 = BuildMI(MBB, MBBI, MI.getDebugLoc(), 0
2713 TII->get(PICAddOpc)) 0
2714 .addReg(DstReg, RegState::Define | getDeadRegState(DstIsDead)) 0
2715 .addReg(DstReg).addImm(LabelId); 0
2716 if (isARM) { 0
2717 MIB3.add(predOps(ARMCC::AL)); 0
2718 if (Opcode == ARM::MOV_ga_pcrel_ldr) 0
2719 MIB3.cloneMemRefs(MI); 0
2720 } ----
2721 MIB3.copyImplicitOps(MI); 0
2722 MI.eraseFromParent(); 0
2723 return true; 0
2724 } ----

2760 unsigned NewOpc = ARM::VLDMDIA; 0
2761 MachineInstrBuilder MIB = ----
2762 BuildMI(MBB, MBBI, MI.getDebugLoc(), TII->get(NewOpc)); 0
2763 unsigned OpIdx = 0; 0
2764 ----
2765 // Grab the Q register destination. ----
2766 bool DstIsDead = MI.getOperand(OpIdx).isDead(); 0
2767 Register DstReg = MI.getOperand(OpIdx++).getReg(); 0
2768 ----
2769 // Copy the source register. ----
2770 MIB.add(MI.getOperand(OpIdx++)); 0
2771 ----
2772 // Copy the predicate operands. ----
2773 MIB.add(MI.getOperand(OpIdx++)); 0
2774 MIB.add(MI.getOperand(OpIdx++)); 0
2775 ----
2776 // Add the destination operands (D subregs). ----
2777 Register D0 = TRI->getSubReg(DstReg, ARM::dsub_0); 0
2778 Register D1 = TRI->getSubReg(DstReg, ARM::dsub_1); 0
2779 MIB.addReg(D0, RegState::Define | getDeadRegState(DstIsDead)) 0
2780 .addReg(D1, RegState::Define | getDeadRegState(DstIsDead)); 0
2781 ----
2782 // Add an implicit def for the super-register. ----
2783 MIB.addReg(DstReg, RegState::ImplicitDefine | getDeadRegState(DstIsDead)); 0
2784 MIB.copyImplicitOps(MI); 0

2802 MIB.add(Dst); 0

2804 // Copy the predicate operands. ----
2805 MIB.add(MI.getOperand(OpIdx++)); 0
2806 MIB.add(MI.getOperand(OpIdx++)); 0

2810 Register D1 = TRI->getSubReg(SrcReg, ARM::dsub_1); 0

3227 bool ARMExpandPseudo::ExpandMBB(MachineBasicBlock &MBB) { 0
3228 bool Modified = false; 0
3229 ----
3230 MachineBasicBlock::iterator MBBI = MBB.begin(), E = MBB.end(); 0
3231 while (MBBI != E) { 0
3232 MachineBasicBlock::iterator NMBBI = std::next(MBBI); 0
3233 Modified |= ExpandMI(MBB, MBBI, NMBBI); 0
3234 MBBI = NMBBI; 0
3235 } ----
3236 ----
3237 return Modified; 0
